item.title: CVE-2020-7371|2024-09-16T22:50:27.553Z -- raise%20it%20solutions -- rits%20browser
item.description: User Interface (UI) Misrepresentation of Critical Information vulnerability in the address bar of the Yandex Browser allows an attacker to obfuscate the true source of data as presented in the browser. This issue affects the RITS Browser version 3.3.9 and prior versions.
